metadata.description: The Poker Protocol Premium collection of NFTs will consist of 777 membership style NFTs giving holders access to the highest APY available for our DeFi service. Your membership grants access to the full Poker Protocol ecosystem including but not limited to: High APY Eth staking, wall street trading calls and yield poker games. Further details on our vision map can be found on our website www.pokerprotocol.io
